node.text: Here’s a breakdown to get the beachy waves I’ve been rocking recently! I’m obsessed with this look and it lasts for daysss. It is my FAVORITE look, please try and let me know how it goes!! Pop in some dry-shampoo in between the layers and don’t forget to wash with @redken hair cleansing cream 1-2 times a month in addition to your usual (semi)daily shampoo routine 🥰🙏🏼 #ad

node.title: Shakira waves tutorial! Ft @redken and a whole lotta hair ❤️

node.text:
*not that I’m an expert at anything but I feel I have this look down alright☺️*
1️⃣quench @tarte moisturizing primer
2️⃣armani luminous silk 5.5 mix with Tarte h2o
3️⃣SHAPE TAPE by tarte cuz I gotta hide these dark circles
4️⃣peach perfect powder
5️⃣sugar rush bronzer
6️⃣tarteist pro glow
7️⃣mac clear brown set + Tarte powder
8️⃣too faced natural lust silk robe
9️⃣tarte maneater mascara
🔟 setting spray - smashbox + Tarte stay spray
.
Lash extensions - @fvckmascara
Hairrr - @hairby_chrissy
.
I use a lot of Tarte goodies, as you can see, and they’ve gifted me with a coupon code for you for the holidays!! “Nikki” will save you 15% at Tarte.com - 🎄✨🎅🏽 Ho Ho Ho merry Christmas amirite LOVE YOU GUYZ

node.text:
I’ve been seeing Landmine (or I’ve always called it a T-bar set up? Same thing I believe) workouts pop up on my feed for a while now so you can say I’ve been ✨influenced✨ 🥰 to add a bit into my routine!! I lack coordination for some, but I enjoyed these 3 in particular to add some interest and change to moves I’m already doing in my regular routine! ❤️
Like and save if you want to remember to add some in as well ☺️

Fit: @gymshark scoop neck training bra and Mercury shorts! Size small in both
Pre-workout: @alaninutrition breezeberry 🫐

node.text:
my sisters kept throwing in this 100 ab challenge to the end of our workouts together, so figured I’d share it with y’all to share the pain 😂🔥🥵
Try it out if you’re looking for an ab burnout!

☆ 100 abs: ☆
10 weighted sit-ups
20 leg lifts
10 scissor kicks
20 v ups
10 bicycles 
20 Toe touches 
10 plank twists 

Wearing @gymshark 
Preworkout @alaninutrition

clips_music_attribution_info.should_mute_audio_reason: Instagram music isn't available in your region.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Nikki Blackketter on August 10, 2021. May be an image of flower.

node.text:
no rules 🌈🌻🍋 wear what makes you happy, do what makes you feel fulfilled, bask in some sunlight today if it’s available, remind people that you’re thinking about them & that you love them 💛💛

(or do none of those bc there are no rules) end of the day YOU DO YOU BOO BOO

LEG DAY ~ q u a d ~ focus 🤎✨🧋
Another leg day in the books 👏 this one I focused mostly on my quads / abductors and they have been sore for 2 days now so mission success 😎 like and save for laterrr!! 💛

circuit one
✨barbell squats x 10-12
✨lateral band walks x 30
repeat 4 times

circuit two
✨lateral static lunge x12 per leg
✨quad extensions x15
✨step ups x12 per leg
repeat 3 times

follow with core work and stretching 🥰

🌿wearing @gymshark scoop neck training bra and vital seamless shorts in size small
🤎preworkout 🫐 breezeberry @alaninutrition 
🎵song: vintage velour by xavy rusan

node.text:
BOOTY WORK🌿🌸🧋
Felt fiiiire after this workout, highly recommend. Saw a @beth_fitnessuk TikTok and got motivated af and then jumped in the gym and did this!! Def save for later if you want to booty pump of your dreams lol 🍑

circuit one
✨Bulgarian split squat x10-12 per leg
✨quad extension x15
✨standing banded kickback x15 per leg
Repeat 3 times

circuit two
✨triple contraction hip thrust x10
✨single leg hip thrust x10 per leg
Repeat 4 times

That’s it! Super challenging, booty pump was UNREALL after, highly recommend 💖

Wearing @gymshark bandeau bra and Mercury shorts, size small
Preworkout: @alaninutrition breezeberry 
Song: shine like diamonds by filthy the kid
